We recommended that the LCE instruct the:

Municipal Planning and Development Office (MPDO), MEO and Local Finance Committee to adequately plan the PPAs under the 20 per cent DF by ensuring the identified projects to be of high-impact, with urgency and implementation-ready and to require the Punong Barangay and other requesters to establish the objectives, scope, duration, issues and risks of the PPAs;

MEO and Local Finance Committee to ensure that the funding costs are assigned to PPAs that have undergone scrutiny and detailed work is mapped-out;

BAC Members and the Implementing Offices to properly plan and schedule all procurement activities pertaining to development projects to pave way for their timely implementation and completion; and

MPDO and MEO to properly schedule and monitor the status of project implementation so that early achievement of its objective would be attained.

